rComments: Writing 2 with Stephanie as a lecturer was an okay class, and she knows what she's talking about.  However, she is also an extremely tough grader when it comes down to essay assignments.

Kresge core with Stephanie was great. She might be a little confusing at times because she's always TOO excited about things. She tries to stop herself from blurting out everything so that the students can try to think and figure out her point. Her only problem is that she can be vague about the main point because of "excitedness." Easy Class.
